<section class="setup" id="setup">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">
      <span class="glow-text">System Audio Setup</span>
    </h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">Visualize Spotify, Apple Music, or any app on macOS</p>
    
    <div class="setup-grid">
      <div class="setup-card">
        <div class="setup-number">1</div>
        <h3>Get a Virtual Audio Device</h3>
        <p>Use one of these tools to route audio:</p>
        <div class="setup-links">
          <a href="https://rogueamoeba.com/loopback/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Loopback <span class="badge">Recommended</span>
          </a>
          <a href="https://rogueamoeba.com/soundsource/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            SoundSource
          </a>
          <a href="https://existential.audio/blackhole/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            BlackHole <span class="badge free">Free</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="setup-card">
        <div class="setup-number">2</div>
        <h3>Set System Input</h3>
        <p>Open System Settings and configure the virtual device:</p>
        <div class="setup-path">
          <code>System Settings → Sound → Input</code>
        </div>
        <p class="setup-note">Select your Loopback or BlackHole device as the input source</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="setup-card">
        <div class="setup-number">3</div>
        <h3>Launch Animus</h3>
        <p>Start the visualizer and play some music. The audio will flow through!</p>
        <div class="setup-tip">
          <strong>Tip:</strong> Use the sensitivity slider to adjust visualization intensity
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .setup {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .setup::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--accent-green), transparent);
  }
  
  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  
  .setup-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }
  
  .setup-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid rgba(168, 224, 99, 0.1);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .setup-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: -1rem;
    left: 2rem;
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 2.5rem;
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    color: var(--bg-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  
  .setup-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    padding-top: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .setup-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .setup-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  
  .setup-links a {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(168, 224, 99, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(168, 224, 99, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }
  
  .setup-links a:hover {
    background: rgba(168, 224, 99, 0.1);
    border-color: var(--accent-green);
  }
  
  .badge {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
    background: var(--accent-gradient);
    color: var(--bg-primary);
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-left: auto;
  }
  
  .badge.free {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a90a4, #67b26f);
  }
  
  .setup-path {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .setup-path code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent-green);
  }
  
  .setup-note {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  
  .setup-tip {
    background: rgba(168, 224, 99, 0.1);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-green);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  
  .setup-tip strong {
    color: var(--accent-green);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .setup-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
